# See https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/getting-started-with-git/ignoring-files for more about ignoring files.

# compiled output
dist
# Un-ignore the pre-built voice companion frontend so deployed snapshots
# always have correct, in-sync index.html + hashed JS/CSS bundles.
# Every Vite build is deterministic (content-hashed), so this is safe.
!artifacts/voice-companion/dist
!artifacts/voice-companion/dist/**
tmp
out-tsc
*.tsbuildinfo
.expo
.expo-shared

# dependencies
node_modules

